{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六回写袁承志与同门、江湖人物相遇，华山武学和木桑道人轻功等线索交错。安小慧等旧事穿插其中，江湖恩义与荒诞趣味并行。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁承志心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温南扬续道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "温仪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温仪冷冷的道：",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温青青哼了一声，道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那便是那柄金蛇剑了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位金蛇郎君大有豪气。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "温仪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温仪道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_xue_yi",
      "speaker_name": "夏雪宜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是金蛇郎君的惯技。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青青道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你六爷爷的尸首！给斩成了八块！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "温仪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温仪道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "温仪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温南扬道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎地他们兄弟这么多？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "温仪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温仪道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青青道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_xue_yi",
      "speaker_name": "夏雪宜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又想：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青青道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温南扬道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的骸骨是袁相公埋葬的，那么我什么事也不必瞒你，只求袁相公待会把他去世时的情形，说给我们母女俩知道⋯⋯那么⋯⋯",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大踏步便向亭外走去。青青道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温仪道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青青道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈，他待你很好啊，这人很有良心。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来在金蛇秘笈中发现的，便是这张宝藏地图。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈妈，你很对。你又做错了什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夏前辈那时候想是已经找到了宝藏？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "令尊是骗他的，不是真心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_xue_yi",
      "speaker_name": "夏雪宜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么下我的毒？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿仪，你把自己的丑事说给外人听，还要脸么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承志大哥不会怕的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "温仪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我就说下去。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "温仪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她向亭外一指，说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青青道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温方达不愿在外人之前多提家门丑事，叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "温仪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承志听到",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "温仪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三字，陡然想起《金蛇秘笈》中详述",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "温仪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "及其破法的记载，恍然大悟：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温方山喝道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈妈！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承志听她话中带着哭声，点头道：",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "承志见她眼光散乱，呼吸急促，已有些神智失常，劝道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿仪，你再胡说八道，可小心着！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我干么小心？你以为我还怕死么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_xue_yi",
      "speaker_name": "夏雪宜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温仪低声道：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_xue_yi",
      "speaker_name": "夏雪宜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "轻轻叹了口气，说道：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_xue_yi",
      "speaker_name": "夏雪宜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五行阵",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温方施阴森森的道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "须得静下来好好想一想，筹思善策。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温方山低声道：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温方达道：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快刀斩乱麻",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心想：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "温青青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只见烛火晃动，已有两支蜡烛熄了，当下站起身来，说道：",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 850,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温方达道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 852,
      "line_end": 852
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却听得温方施道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 882,
      "line_end": 882
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大声喝道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 882,
      "line_end": 882
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一瞥之间见到了袁承志，更是不解：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 912,
      "line_end": 912
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "便道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 914,
      "line_end": 914
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "眼光向着地下一块块的金条一扫，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 916,
      "line_end": 916
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温方山道：",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 924
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "荣彩双手一拱，说道：",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 924
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见金条散在地下，说道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 970,
      "line_end": 970
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁承志道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 990,
      "line_end": 990
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "黄真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄真道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 992,
      "line_end": 992
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不敢当！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1004,
      "line_end": 1004
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "黄真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄真又骂：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1006,
      "line_end": 1006
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁承志向崔希敏笑道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1008,
      "line_end": 1008
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "崔希敏道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1010,
      "line_end": 1010
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吕七先生又是磔磔两声怪笑，转头向荣彩道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1022,
      "line_end": 1022
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "荣彩喝道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1024,
      "line_end": 1024
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_xiao_hui",
      "speaker_name": "安小慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "崔希敏道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1054,
      "line_end": 1054
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "突然拔起身子，站到了两块金条之上，右手中的旱烟袋点着另一块金条，说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1060,
      "line_end": 1060
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说话可不许反悔。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1066,
      "line_end": 1066
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "荣彩只得跟着干笑一阵，心中却也颇感疑惑。崔希敏道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1068,
      "line_end": 1068
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "黄真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "崔希敏破口大骂：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1084,
      "line_end": 1084
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "黄真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄真伸手在他腰里一捏，腿上一戳，解开了闭住的穴道，说道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1086,
      "line_end": 1086
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是师弟，该当先上！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1096,
      "line_end": 1096
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "袁承志也放低了声音道：",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1106,
      "line_end": 1106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_cheng_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "袁承志",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄真见他执意要上，心想初生犊儿不怕虎，不便拂了他少年人的兴头，便道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1108,
      "line_end": 1108
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吕七先生！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1172,
      "line_end": 1172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "黄真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄真一本正经的答道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1178,
      "line_end": 1178
    }
